extendedInfo.description: Fancy Jigsaw is a classic puzzle game. Drag the Brush work paintings.pieces to the right place to re-establish the full picture. Don't sweat it if you are unable to solve the puzzle easily. You can use the peek button to preview the original image.There are 100 levels in this game. The further you advance, the more challenging the puzzle becomes. This app also allows you to save the Brush work paintings to your SD .The Brush work paintings is traditional Chinese way to depict pictures superbly. China has long history of paiting, from the Warrring state period to Song Dynasty, the brush work paiting skill has developed from scratch to mature. In brush work painting, no matter people, or flower, all seeking for similar to its original models. In this series we selected some representative paintings for your enjoyment.Cool Features Include:- More than 100 pictures of Brush work paintings.- Multiple difficulty levels (from 3*3 to the most difficult 7*7).- Save to phone album function.- Images gallery and difficulty selection.Fancy JigSaw is suitable for a wide range of audiences, Many different modes and pictures in the game will keep you excited and entertained for a long time.Keywords:puzzle,puzzles,Jigsaw,games,brainfun,funny,Brush work paintings,entertainment,wallpapers,animal,nature.
